description: Dashboard visualizes Konflux clusters loadtest single-arch probe results. Related Horreum test is https://horreum.corp.redhat.com/test/372 with filter by label `.repo_type = nodejs-devfile-sample` and right `__parameters_options_PipelineRepoTemplatingSourceDir`.

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
    EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM start) AS "time",
    CASE
        WHEN '${smoothing}' = '3 hours' THEN AVG((label_values->>'__results_measurements_KPI_mean')::DOUBLE PRECISION) OVER (ORDER BY start RANGE '3 hours' PRECEDING)
        WHEN '${smoothing}' = '12 hours' THEN AVG((label_values->>'__results_measurements_KPI_mean')::DOUBLE PRECISION) OVER (ORDER BY start RANGE '12 hours' PRECEDING)
        WHEN '${smoothing}' = '1 day' THEN AVG((label_values->>'__results_measurements_KPI_mean')::DOUBLE PRECISION) OVER (ORDER BY start RANGE '1 day' PRECEDING)
        WHEN '${smoothing}' = '3 days' THEN AVG((label_values->>'__results_measurements_KPI_mean')::DOUBLE PRECISION) OVER (ORDER BY start RANGE '3 days' PRECEDING)
        ELSE (label_values->>'__results_measurements_KPI_mean')::DOUBLE PRECISION
    END AS "value",
    '__results_measurements_KPI_mean' as "metric"
FROM
    data
WHERE
    horreum_testid = 372
    AND label_values->>'.metadata.env.MEMBER_CLUSTER' = ${member_cluster}
    AND $__timeFilter(start)
    AND label_values->>'.repo_type' = 'nodejs-devfile-sample' AND label_values->>'.results.measurements.KPI.mean' != '-1' AND (label_values->>'__parameters_options_PipelineRepoTemplatingSourceDir' IS NULL OR label_values->>'__parameters_options_PipelineRepoTemplatingSourceDir' = '' OR label_values->>'__parameters_options_PipelineRepoTemplatingSourceDir' = 'nodejs-devfile-sample-test/' OR label_values->>'__parameters_options_PipelineRepoTemplatingSourceDir' = 'nodejs-devfile-sample-SingleArch/')
